Definition: highly offensive
Example: arousing aversion or disgust; a disgusting smell; distasteful language; a loathsome disease; the idea of eating meat is repellent to me; revolting food; a wicked stench
Synonyms: noun, attribute, disgustingness, disgustful, distasteful, distastefulness, foul, loathly, loathsome, loathsomeness, repellent, verb, perception, repel, emotion, repellant, repelling, revolting, skanky, substance, skank, wicked, wickedness, yucky, highly, offensive, arousing, aversion, or, disgust, a, smell, language, disease, the, idea, of, eating, meat, is, to, me, food, stench
Category: adj.all
